title: Lost Dogs Discography 1992-2010 (16 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
LOST DOGS DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 16 releases...

 * 1992 - Harvest Moon Festival
 * 1992 - Scenic Routes
 * 1993 - Little Red Riding Hood
 * 1999 - Live In Phoenix
 * 1999 - The Best Of The Lost Dogs
 * 2000 - Gift Horse
 * 2001 - Real Men Cry
 * 2002 - Green Room Serenade Part Tour
 * 2003 - Nazarene Crying Towel
 * 2003 - Via Chicago
 * 2004 - Mutt
 * 2005 - Island Dreams
 * 2006 - The Lost Cabin And The Mystery Trees
 * 2006 - Via Chicago - All We Left Unsaid
 * 2007 - We Like To Have Christmas
 * 2010 - Old Angel

Lost Dogs are an American musical super group formed in 1991, comprising vocalists, songwriters, and guitarists from multiple Christian alternative rock bands.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
